Package Progress

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Class
    Represents a real-life class that a student is enrolled in so they have access to the supplemental materials the instructor has provided.
    Graph
    This abstract class provides default implementations for most of the methods used for the graphs of students' progress and scores.
    LeftSideBar
    Rectangular content section on the left side of the page that contains tabs with different view options and other information.
    List
    Expandable list type that will be displayed in the left side bar.
    MainContent
    Largest rectangular section on the page that will display content such as graphs and statistics.
    OverviewTutorialGraph
    Bar chart that displays the average scores of all tutorials an instructor has created.
    Student
    A student object that contains the name of the student and other information.
    StudentGraph
    Bar chart that displays the quiz scores of the tutorials the student has completed.
    Tab
    A sub-section of the left side bar that contains expandable lists.
    TutorialData
    Contains all data from a tutorial
